graph TD
    subgraph Data Collection and Preprocessing
        A[Start] --> B[Data Collection]
        B --> |360° Images| C[Image Preprocessing]
        B --> |Product Labels| D[Text Extraction OCR]
        C --> E[Image Augmentation]
        D --> F[Text Normalization]
        E --> G[Dataset Creation]
        F --> G
    end

    subgraph Model Development and Training
        G --> H[YOLO Model Selection]
        H --> I[Hyperparameter Tuning]
        I --> J[Model Training]
        J --> K{Validation}
        K -->|Not Satisfied| I
        K -->|Satisfied| L[Trained YOLO Model]
    end

    subgraph Multimodal Fusion
        L --> M[Visual Feature Extraction]
        G --> N[Text Feature Extraction]
        M --> O[Feature Fusion]
        N --> O
        O --> P[Multimodal Classifier]
    end

    subgraph Evaluation and Deployment
        P --> Q[Test Set Evaluation]
        Q --> R[Performance Analysis]
        R --> S{Meet Requirements?}
        S -->|No| T[Model Refinement]
        T --> I
        S -->|Yes| U[Deploy Model]
    end

    style A fill:#f9d5e5,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style G fill:#eeac99,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style L fill:#e06377,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style P fill:#5b9aa0,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style U fill:#d6eaf8,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px

    classDef process fill:#f9f9f9,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px;
    class B,C,D,E,F,H,I,J,M,N,O,Q,R,T process;

    classDef decision fill:#ffe6e6,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px;
    class K,S decision;
